OL,6,FThe West of Scotland league side said:
OL,7,F"Charlie was more than just a player.
OL,8,FHe was an absolute warrior, a pillar
OL,9,Fof our club, and a true inspiration to
OL,10,Fall who had the privilege of knowing
OL,11,Fhim.
OL,13,F"His strength, determination, and
OL,14,Fheart both on and off the pitch
OL,15,Fdefined him, and his loss leaves a
OL,16,Fvoid that words cannot fill.
OL,18,F"We will ensure his legacy lives on,
OL,19,Fhonouring his memory in every way we
OL,20,Fcan.
